<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Password Reset</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; background-color: #f8f9fa; color: #000000;">
<div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.95) 0%, rgba(248,249,250,0.98) 100%); padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(128, 0, 32, 0.2); border: 1px solid rgba(128, 0, 32, 0.3);">
    <h2 style="color: #800020; font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 20px;">Password Reset Request</h2>

    <p style="color: #000000; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 15px;">Hello <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>

    <p style="color: #000000; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 15px;">We received a request to reset the password for your SendItCourier account. Please use the following One-Time Password (OTP) to proceed:</p>

    <div style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #800020; text-align: center; padding: 15px; background-color: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; border: 1px solid rgba(128, 0, 32, 0.3);">
        <%= otp %>
    </div>

    <p style="color: #000000; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 15px;"><strong>Note:</strong> This OTP will expire in <%= expiresIn %> minutes. Enter it in the password reset form on our platform to reset your password.</p>

    <p style="color: #000000; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 15px;">If you did not request a password reset, please disregard this email. Your account remains secure.</p>

    <p style="color: #000000; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 15px;">Thank you,<br />
        The SendItCourier Team</p>
</div>

<div style="font-size: 12px; color: #6c757d; margin-top: 30px; text-align: center;">
    &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> SendItCourier. All rights reserved.
</div>
</body>
</html>